<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
     <meta charset="UTF-8">
     <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
     <title>Oups ! Erreur 500 - Ndressilik</title>
     <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
     <style>
          body,
          html {
               height: 100%;
               margin: 0;
               font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
               background-color: #f0f7f4;
               display: flex;
               align-items: center;
               justify-content: center;
               color: #333;
               overflow: hidden;
          }

          .container {
               text-align: center;
               padding: 2rem;
               max-width: 600px;
               position: relative;
          }

          h1 {
               font-size: 3rem;
               margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
               color: #3FB1B0;
          }

          .error-code {
               font-size: 1.5rem;
               font-weight: 600;
               color: #FF6B6B;
               margin-bottom: 1rem;
          }

          p {
               font-size: 1.2rem;
               margin-bottom: 2rem;
               line-height: 1.6;
          }

          .btn {
               display: inline-block;
               padding: 12px 24px;
               background-color: #3FB1B0;
               color: white;
               text-decoration: none;
               border-radius: 30px;
               font-size: 1.1rem;
               font-weight: 600;
               transition: all 0.3s ease;
               box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
          }

          .btn:hover,
          .btn:focus {
               background-color: #2C7A7B;
               transform: translateY(-2px);
               box-shadow: 0 6px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
          }

          .dog {
               width: 200px;
               height: 200px;
               margin: 0 auto 2rem;
               position: relative;
               cursor: pointer;
          }

          .dog-body {
               width: 120px;
               height: 60px;
               background-color: #A0522D;
               border-radius: 50px 50px 0 0;
               position: absolute;
               bottom: 0;
               left: 40px;
          }

          .dog-head {
               width: 80px;
               height: 80px;
               background-color: #A0522D;
               border-radius: 50%;
               position: absolute;
               top: 40px;
               left: 60px;
          }

          .dog-ear {
               width: 30px;
               height: 40px;
               background-color: #8B4513;
               border-radius: 0 0 15px 15px;
               position: absolute;
               top: -10px;
          }

          .dog-ear.left {
               left: 5px;
               transform: rotate(-30deg);
          }

          .dog-ear.right {
               right: 5px;
               transform: rotate(30deg);
          }

          .dog-eye {
               width: 12px;
               height: 12px;
               background-color: #000;
               border-radius: 50%;
               position: absolute;
               top: 30px;
          }

          .dog-eye.left {
               left: 20px;
          }

          .dog-eye.right {
               right: 20px;
          }

          .dog-nose {
               width: 16px;
               height: 8px;
               background-color: #000;
               border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
               position: absolute;
               bottom: 15px;
               left: 32px;
          }

          .dog-tail {
               width: 15px;
               height: 60px;
               background-color: #8B4513;
               border-radius: 15px;
               position: absolute;
               bottom: 10px;
               right: -5px;
               transform-origin: bottom center;
               animation: wagTail 0.5s infinite alternate;
          }

          @keyframes wagTail {
               0% {
                    transform: rotate(-10deg);
               }

               100% {
                    transform: rotate(10deg);
               }
          }

          .paw-print {
               position: absolute;
               opacity: 0;
               transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
          }

          @media (max-width: 480px) {
               h1 {
                    font-size: 2.5rem;
               }

               .error-code {
                    font-size: 1.2rem;
               }

               p {
                    font-size: 1rem;
               }

               .dog {
                    transform: scale(0.8);
               }
          }
     </style>
</head>

<body>
     <div class="container">
          <div class="dog" id="dog">
               <div class="dog-body"></div>
               <div class="dog-head">
                    <div class="dog-ear left"></div>
                    <div class="dog-ear right"></div>
                    <div class="dog-eye left"></div>
                    <div class="dog-eye right"></div>
                    <div class="dog-nose"></div>
               </div>
               <div class="dog-tail"></div>
          </div>
          <h1>Oups ! Notre chien a fait une bÃªtise</h1>
          <p class="error-code">Erreur 500</p>
          <p>Il semble que notre serveur ait besoin d'un peu plus de dressage. Nous travaillons Ã  corriger ce problÃ¨me aussi vite que possible !</p>
          <p>En attendant, pourquoi ne pas retourner Ã  l'accueil et explorer d'autres parties de notre site ?</p>
          <a href="/" class="btn">Retourner Ã  l'accueil</a>
     </div>

     <script>
          document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', (event) => {
               const dog = document.getElementById('dog');
               const container = document.querySelector('.container');

               function createPawPrint(x, y) {
                    const pawPrint = document.createElement('div');
                    pawPrint.className = 'paw-print';
                    pawPrint.style.left = x + 'px';
                    pawPrint.style.top = y + 'px';
                    pawPrint.innerHTML = 'ðŸ¾';
                    pawPrint.style.fontSize = '24px';
                    container.appendChild(pawPrint);

                    setTimeout(() => {
                         pawPrint.style.opacity = '1';
                    }, 50);

                    setTimeout(() => {
                         pawPrint.style.opacity = '0';
                         setTimeout(() => {
                              container.removeChild(pawPrint);
                         }, 500);
                    }, 2000);
               }

               function handleInteraction(event) {
                    const rect = container.getBoundingClientRect();
                    const x = event.clientX - rect.left;
                    const y = event.clientY - rect.top;
                    createPawPrint(x, y);
               }

               // Handle both click and touch events
               dog.addEventListener('click', handleInteraction);
               dog.addEventListener('touchstart', (e) => {
                    e.preventDefault(); // Prevent default touch behavior
                    handleInteraction(e.touches[0]);
               });

               // Initial animation
               container.style.opacity = '0';
               container.style.transform = 'translateY(20px)';
               container.style.transition = 'opacity 0.5s ease-out, transform 0.5s ease-out';

               setTimeout(() => {
                    container.style.opacity = '1';
                    container.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
               }, 100);
          });
     </script>
</body>

</html>